description:
Ordisky is an collection for the IB whisky on Ordinals.Tasting notes of The Whisky Agency Cask#700022:
Nose: Sea breeze, bonfire, lemon peel, old cigar box.
Palate:Golden Kiwi, apricot, fresh lemon grass juice, mango.
Finish: long and soft smoke, Himalaya salt, old leather,coffee bean.
name: Ordisky
